<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-1014] Problem invoking a method with arrays as arguments</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-1014</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It seems to be impossible to invoke methods that take arrays as arguments. See the included test case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>winxp, jdk 142_08</environment>
        <key id="12811688">GROOVY-1014</key>
            <summary>Problem invoking a method with arrays as arguments</summary>
